<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12 col-md-6 offset-md-3 text-center">
    <div class="form-title">Go Meat-Free</div>
    <div class="form-desc">
    <p>Livestock generates more greenhouse gases than all the cars and trucks in the world.  Most of it comes from carbon dioxide and nitrous oxide gases generated by manure. The single most important step an individual can take to reduce global warming is to adopt a vegetarian diet.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="firstscale mb-5">
      <div class="col-12 px-2 mb-3">
        <div class="row range card-range">
          <div class="col my-2 w-40">
          <%= image_tag("difficulty.png", size: "23x20")%>
            <label for="exampleRangeDifficulty">Difficulty</label>
              <div class="slider">
                  <div class="slider-value" style="width:75%; height:5px; color:white;">.</div>
                </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col my-2 w-40 mb-5">
          <%= image_tag("world.png", size: "18x18")%>
            <label for="exampleRangeImpact">Impact</label>
              <div class="slider">
                  <div class="slider-value" style="width:50%; height:5px; color:white;">.</div>
              </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="secondscale">
      <div class="col-12 px-2 mb-3">
        <label for="exampleRangeImpact">For how many weeks do you want to do this challenge?</label>
          <input type="range" class="custom-range" id="exampleRangeMood" step="10" required min="0" max="50" value="0">

        <label for="exampleRangeImpact">How many exeptions do you want to add?</label>
          <input type="range" class="custom-range" id="exampleRangeMood" step="10" required min="0" max="50" value="0">
      </div>
    </div>

      <div class="button button-large mt-3 mb-3" style="margin: 20px auto;">
        <%= link_to 'Start Challenge', root_path %>
      </div>

  </div>
</div>
